Hash Map / Frequency Count (Optimal)
Count characters in s.
Subtract counts using t.
If all counts = 0 â†’ return true.
Time: O(n)
Space: O(1) for 26 letters (or O(k) for general Unicode).



code:
class Solution{
public:
    bool isAnagram(string s,string t){
        if(s.size()!=t.size()) return false;
        vector<int> count(26,0);
        for(char c:s) count[c-'a']++;
        for(char c:t){
            count[c-'a']--;
            if(count[c-'a']<0) return false;
        }
        return true;
    }
};
